GRAPHIC file commands                   Press ESC to return
=====================
                        PCX  Color-TX
   UP / DOWN             x     x        SELECTS hypertext jumps
   RIGHT (or ENTER)      x     x        EXECUTES hypertext jump
   LEFT (or ESC)         x     x        RETURNS to parent hypertext jump
   Ctrl-Home             x     x        RETURNS to initial screen
   L                     -     x        LOOKUP words in glossary
   M or F6               x     x        MARKS file - lists jumps to such files
   F8                    -     x        COPY selected text to CLIP.TXT file
   P                     x     x        PRINTS the file
   Q, X, or Alt-X        x     x        QUITS the program

   G                     -     x        GOTO another file (such as SEARCH.TXT)
   D                     -     x        DOS/PROGRAM call (such as DIR)
   V                     x     x        VIEW previous selected hypertext jumps
   H                     -     x        List files with jumps TO current file
   C                     -     x        COLOR settings
   Alt-F6 / Alt-F8       x     x        Clears BOOKMARK.TXT / CLIP.TXT files
   Home / End            x     -        Selects FIRST / LAST hypertext jump
   Ctrl-RIGHT / LEFT     x     -        SCROLLS graphic horizontally
   PgUp / PgDn           x     -        SCROLLS graphic vertically
   Press 1-9, 0          x     -        BRANCHES on screen displayed numbers

